<%- include('partials/header')  %>
<main class="process-page">
    <h1>How Our Loan Process Works</h1>

    <section class="process-step">
        <h2>1. Create an Account</h2>
        <p>
            Start by creating an account with us. Your account allows you to apply for loans
            and track the status of your application at any time.
        </p>
    </section>

    <section class="process-step">
        <h2>2. Submit Your Loan Application</h2>
        <p>
            After creating your account, you can apply for the type of loan that best fits your needs.
            We currently offer several loan options including auto loans, personal loans, and mortgage loans.
        </p>
    </section>

    <section class="process-step">
        <h2>3. Application Review</h2>
        <p>
            Once your application is submitted, our credit manager will carefully review your
            information and supporting details.
        </p>
    </section>

    <section class="process-step">
        <h2>4. Quick Decision</h2>
        <p>
            Our goal is to provide fast and reliable service. In many cases, you will receive a
            loan decision within minutes. We pride ourselves on providing some of the best loan
            servicing in America.
        </p>
    </section>

    <section class="final-step">
        <h2><a href="/register">Ready for Funding? Make an Account Here!</a></h2>
    </section>
</main>

<%- include('partials/footer')  %>